# Project-wide registry namespace for `docker push` / `docker pull`.
#
# Used by ops/release.sh, ops/prod/push_image.sh, and the dev / prod
# target host lifecycle.sh (auto-pull on prod `start` / `restart`).
#
# Resolution chain (highest priority first):
#   1. Shell env: `export DOCKER_REGISTRY=ccr.ccs.tencentyun.com/your-ns`
#   2. This file (REGISTRY) — first non-empty, non-comment DOCKER_REGISTRY= line
#   3. Auto-detect (lib.sh → detect_default_registry) — docker.io/$USER or empty
#
# Format: a namespace prefix prepended to `image:tag` for push/pull.
#   docker.io/zhangyu528           — Docker Hub (公共,慢,要登录)
#   ccr.ccs.tencentyun.com/your-ns — 腾讯云 TCR (推荐,见下文)
#   ghcr.io/myorg                  — GitHub Container Registry
#   registry.gitlab.com/mygroup    — GitLab Container Registry
#
# This file is COMMITTED to git. It is shared project config, not a
# personal secret. Personal secrets (postgres password, AI keys, TTS keys)
# live in GitHub Environments and are fetched per-session via
# scripts/secrets/fetch_secrets.sh.
#
# Recommended: Tencent Cloud TCR (容器镜像服务)
# ------------------------------------------------
# If your prod host is a Tencent Cloud CVM, **use TCR**. It is the
# recommended prod path because:
#   • CVM 跟 TCR 在同一 VPC 时,`docker pull` 走内网,无公网流量费
#   • 个人版免费额度够个人项目用
#   • 可用 CVM 的 RAM role 免密登录,不需要 docker login
#   • 跟 TencentDB 同控制台,运维心智统一
#
# Setup:
#   1. 腾讯云控制台 → 容器镜像服务 TCR → 创建个人版实例(选最近的 region)
#   2. 在实例里建命名空间(例如 type-any-language)
#   3. 创建一个访问凭证(临时 token,或给 CVM 绑 RAM role)
#   4. 把下面的 DOCKER_REGISTRY 行取消注释,填你的 namespace:
#         DOCKER_REGISTRY=ccr.ccs.tencentyun.com/your-tcr-id/type-any-language
#   5. 第一次手动 docker login 一次(或 CVM 用 RAM role 自动认证)
#
# Leave this file empty (no uncommented DOCKER_REGISTRY= line) to fall
# back to detect_default_registry() (docker.io/$USER on most dev hosts)
# or local-only mode (no push, no auto-pull). Uncomment + edit the
# line below to pin a shared registry for the team.

# DOCKER_REGISTRY=docker.io/youruser